@node Main "NixNext - Documentation"

                              'NixNext' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'NixNext' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to remove tiles of
the same type that are placed next to each other. When you click on
a tile, all tiles that are next to the clicked tiles will 'blow-up'.
If one or more of these tiles are of the same type as the one you
clicked, these will be removed and will be replaced by new tiles.
However, if tiles are of different type, they will reappear where
they were located.

  As you get points according to the number of removed tiles, try
to remove as many tiles at a time as possible...

  Have fun!

